Create complete cases

Source: R/create.R
create_complete_cases.Rd

Creates a complete data set without NA values and appropriate indices

Usage

create_complete_cases(cases)

Arguments

cases

data frame with a column "confirm" that may contain NA values

Value

A data frame without NA values, with two columns: confirm (number)
